The paper deals with visual retrieval tasks, specifically image-to-video search, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses indexing and representation techniques, which are common topics in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the complexity and query processing time, which are related to data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
